    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在被人遗忘的瓦莱里科国度，道路龟裂，店面褪色，希望匮乏。<strong>但你拥有拯救它的力量。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到全球首款卡车运输角色扮演游戏。</strong>在这段旅程中，你的运输不仅赚取金钱——更重建社区，恢复经济，缔造传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>运送的不仅是货物。更是希望。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的使命并非将货物运往无名仓库，而是运送修复这片破碎土地的基石。见证关键运输带来的世界变迁：尘封的废弃建筑焕发新颜，沉寂的商铺重燃生机，城镇地标在点滴修复中重现荣光。在《公路卡车司机》中，你的影响真实可感，触手可及。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/9b44212f7639fd4cd405979739b45a93.poster.avif?t=1769085390\" width=780 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/9b44212f7639fd4cd405979739b45a93.webm?t=1769085390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/9b44212f7639fd4cd405979739b45a93.mp4?t=1769085390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为卡车司机，而非仅仅驾驶卡车。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅途最珍贵的篇章，往往藏在沿途的停驻。停好卡车，走出驾驶室，用双脚探索世界。走进商店补给物资，在路边摊享用美食，或探访废品场寻觅稀有零件。建立人际关系，管理个人需求，体验超越公路的深度沉浸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/cb776268f4c88a4ef2cd06d2c2039d35.poster.avif?t=1769085390\" width=780 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/cb776268f4c88a4ef2cd06d2c2039d35.webm?t=1769085390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/cb776268f4c88a4ef2cd06d2c2039d35.mp4?t=1769085390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的卡车，你的传奇。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在真正的角色扮演游戏中，你的成长至关重要。卡车既是值得信赖的伙伴，也是改变命运的利器。深入探索深度定制系统，彻底改造卡车外观，精细调校性能表现。升级引擎提升载重能力，调校悬挂征服险峻丛林路，打造独一无二的视觉风格。从发动机缸体到仪表盘摆件，打造承载你传奇的座驾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/f1c9a4690adfe5118620ed2d1dd3ddc1.poster.avif?t=1769085390\" width=780 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/f1c9a4690adfe5118620ed2d1dd3ddc1.webm?t=1769085390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/f1c9a4690adfe5118620ed2d1dd3ddc1.mp4?t=1769085390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创建专属卡车运输帝国。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位传奇都需要据点。接管废弃的荒芜机场，将其改造为卡车运输帝国的繁荣核心。建造并升级专业工作站，解锁高级维修与改装选项。投资社区将获得回报——当地企业创造的收益将助你成为瓦莱里科最受尊敬的卡车司机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/78a805e6b7747e408cde160bf194509b.poster.avif?t=1769085390\" width=780 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/78a805e6b7747e408cde160bf194509b.webm?t=1769085390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333190/extras/78a805e6b7747e408cde160bf194509b.mp4?t=1769085390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>您的旅程即将启程：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重塑开放世界：</strong>通过实际行动影响经济，见证环境随您的决策而变化。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验真实生活：</strong>徒步探索，进食休憩，与众多令人难忘的角色及任务发布者互动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深度定制：</strong>打造梦想卡车，通过丰富的机械与外观升级定义您的驾驶风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经营运输帝国：</strong>从尘土飞扬的简易机场起步，将卡车运输事业发展成物流巨头。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>惬意旅程：</strong>沉浸于南美风情美景，体验完整的昼夜循环与动态天气系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>缔造传奇：</strong>每个抉择都至关重要，每趟运输都意义非凡，你的传奇此刻启程。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>道路在召唤。立即将《公路卡车司机：新起点》加入愿望清单。</strong></p>",
